{
  "id": "adv_event_2501_01_01",
  "title": "お正月の\n生放送",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……\n今日の自主練はこんなところかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew…\nI guess that’s enough self-practice for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.0481632233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "え……そう？　まだ{user}さんとの\n打ち合わせまで時間あるし、続けても大丈夫だよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… really? We still have time before the meeting\nwith {user}-san‚ so it’s fine if we keep going‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2481630803,
      "endTime": 14.3554874899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "けど、やり過ぎはいかんよ。昨日も夜遅かったんやし\n打ち合わせの時間までしっかりストレッチしときましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But overdoing it ain’t good. We were up late last night too.\nLet’s stretch properly until the meeting time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5421540421,
      "endTime": 23.329047696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "最近ますます体力がついたから\n動き足りない気持ちは、分かるけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been building more stamina lately—\nso I understand wanting to move more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5357142291,
      "endTime": 28.766689189399997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうなんだけど……さっきのステップのところ\n忘れないうちにもっと完成度高めたくって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ but… that step earlier—\nI want to perfect it more before I forget…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9600223702,
      "endTime": 36.8195707482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、時間ギリギリまで練習したいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to practice until the last moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0195705575,
      "endTime": 40.7495253247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれの言いたいことは、よく分かる\nけど焦り過ぎは良くないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand exactly how you feel‚ Sumire.\nBut pushing yourself too hard isn’t good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9628586771,
      "endTime": 46.6945140841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは体が資本やからな\n休む時はちゃんと休んで、ケアをする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your body is your asset as an idol.\nSo when it’s time to rest‚ you rest—and take care.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8878472648,
      "endTime": 53.6391397795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "闇雲にトレーニングを重ねるだけやなくて\nそういうところに高い意識を持つんも大事って話",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It ain’t just about training recklessly.\nHaving that kind of awareness is important too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8391399703,
      "endTime": 61.2921102842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4入りを目指すのなら、なおのこと……ね\nそれに私達はともかく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially if you’re aiming for BIG4…\nBesides‚ for us it’s one thing‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4854433697,
      "endTime": 68.08059078870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれはまだ、中学生だからね\n成長期真っ只中の今、無理して故障させたくないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ you’re still a middle schooler.\nIn the middle of your growth‚ I don’t want you to push too hard and get hurt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2872572264,
      "endTime": 75.675216516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……それはそうかもしれないけど\n……で、でも中学生だからって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That might be true‚\n…b-but just because I’m a middle schooler…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8618833544,
      "endTime": 83.6347179415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "怪我が一生の傷になることもあるしなぁ\nもちろん、うちらも怪我には注意せんとやけど。な？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Injuries can stay with you for life‚ you know.\nOf course‚ we gotta watch out too. Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8280511222,
      "endTime": 92.82877667759999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、分かった\n心配してくれて、ありがとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. I get it.\nThanks for worrying about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0154432299,
      "endTime": 99.8219511034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "（そう……二人は私のこと、心配してくれてるだけ）\n（対等の仲間として見てくれてるからこそ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yeah… they’re just worried about me.）\n（Because they see me as an equal member…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0086178464,
      "endTime": 109.48444582650001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "（それでも、不安に思っちゃうんだよ）\n（……子供扱いされちゃってるのかな？　……って）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And yet… I still get anxious.）\n（…Like— are they treating me like a kid?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6777791025,
      "endTime": 117.735534382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9722009343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私達に、生放送バラエティ番組のMC依頼……ですか\nそれも、年始に放送する特番の？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A request for us to MC a live variety show…?\nAnd it’s even for a New Year’s special?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0222009343,
      "endTime": 129.2074844046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.172610521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "依頼主は、以前瑠依に生放送音楽特番の\n出演を依頼してきたプロデューサーだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The requester is the producer who previously asked Rui\nto appear on that live music show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.414151033,
      "endTime": 135.1813393912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3746727628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……！！　あの時の……。いただいてたメッセージ通り\nまた依頼して下さったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!! From back then… Just like they said in their message‚\nthey’ve reached out to us again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3746727628,
      "endTime": 142.65914313040003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8658097588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなゲストが様々な企画に挑戦。その過程や\n結果を視聴者に届け、元気を与える番組……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A show where different guests take on various challenges‚\nencouraging the viewers by sharing the process and results…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8658097588,
      "endTime": 152.73946011889998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13384.190241200002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.9527934714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "年の初めにピッタリな番組だね！　しかも、企画書には\n私達もそれぞれ企画に挑戦するって書いてあるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s perfect for New Year’s! And the proposal says\nwe each get our own challenge to attempt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9527934714,
      "endTime": 161.729459922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.9427929882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちら三人でメインMCしながらやと、段取りが\n大変そうやけど……チャレンジのし甲斐はあるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being the three main MCs while challenging stuff—\nit sounds tough‚ but worth the challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.9427929882,
      "endTime": 169.6915005688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.8981673881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それに、前回断ってしまった\nプロデューサーからの、ありがたい依頼だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. And since we declined the last offer‚\nthis is a valuable request from them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8981673881,
      "endTime": 176.0947433159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "私達も全力で、挑戦しましょう\n{user}さん、私達を出させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So let’s give it our all.\n{user}-san‚ please let us take the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.2814101541,
      "endTime": 182.91859839789998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.6868086017
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.1819318458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "……って訳で。うちらが番組内でなんの企画に\n挑戦するか、さっそく話し合いましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ let’s talk about which challenges\nwe’ll take on in the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
